info.name: Google Custom Background
info.description:
Over 3000 lines of code.
Its isn't 100% complete but most of the features are supported(fe. google translate widget, weather etc.)

Supports:
-Google Maps
-Google Maps iframe
-Captcha
-News
-Settings

Partial Support:
-Flights
-Books
-Shopping
-Finance
